{"tid":883142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喺市政打排球嗰陣 隔離場個大叔...","createTime":"2018-10-30T15:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T15:50:14.000Z","uid":164163,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"94f8bc0b38b479b8b6cfe7383199af6e8d40facf","tid":883142,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"我啱啱先登記做連登囡 有樣嘢想同大家分享<br />\n<br />\n我讀中西區女校嘅 今年中四 係學校排球隊副隊員 可能有打開排球+發育嘅關係個patpat生得有啲翹 (即係有肉地) <br />\n<br />\n今日去市政練波嗰陣 隔離場有個阿叔 應該係啲羽毛球教練嚟 我一入到場佢不斷咁住我 我同我個fd講 佢哋話我諗多咗啦你 戀童pig咩你估佢 <br />\n<br />\n當我開始淡化咗件事嗰陣 我行去更衣室嗰陣 佢跟住我後面講咗句&quot;X你啊 個屎忽咁撚大&quot; <br />\n<br />\n直到而家都仲有啲唔開心 佢咁講咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0895075d802dc4f492d3fc05377dc03b4e144c71","tid":883142,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e196f16457ab439009dcb5f77fb3c8a1f681089","tid":883142,"uid":15289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:08:35.000Z","msg":"人地都係講事實姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7ab54964b540d2360d4368e06061dd623d9d70","tid":883142,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"#youtoo"},{"pid":"c9df588a289d5c9c607e14727645d1db90f33402","tid":883142,"uid":89229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm